 large N theories,\nthrough the AdS/CFT correspondence, to decoupled field theories on AdS_5.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 3 Feb 2017 08:56:03 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 25 May 2017 14:06:44 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-03-07"}
